In order to prove completeness of [[BCP]], we have to consider the cousins of merge

[[Left Merge]]: $$\Vdash$$ (not this symbol but its L with another vertical bit) (first action left)

[[Communication Merge]]: $$|$$ (first action communication)


$$x \| y = x \Vdash y + y \Vdash x + x | y$$